live-installer (2010.11.21~kazsid0) unstable; urgency=low

  * debian/control:
    - Bump Standards-Version to 3.9.1
    - Add Homepage, Vcs-Git and Vcs-Browser fields
    - Build depend on debhelper >=7
    - Add gksu package to binary dependencies of live-installer
    - Add ${misc:Depends} to binary dependencies of both packages
    - Add me as maintainer
  * debian/rules:
    - remove configure, configure-stamp, build-stamp targets
    - move binary packages building to binary-indep
    - move packages files installation to debian/*.install
    - use dh_installinit and dh_installmenu to install live-installer init
      script and menu file respectively
    - install lintian overrides:
      - live-installer: binary-without-manpage usr/bin/live-installer
      - live-installer: binary-without-manpage usr/bin/live-installer-dm
      - live-installer: desktop-command-not-in-package
        /usr/share/applications/live-installer-launcher.desktop gksudo
      - live-installer: menu-command-not-in-package
        /usr/share/menu/live-installer:5 /usr/bin/gksudo
      - live-installer-slideshow: embedded-javascript-library *
    - remove useless debhelper scripts invocation
  * debian/postinst: update in accordance with debian/rules changes. Also
    rename as live-installer.postinst
  * Add debian/live-installer.{prerm,postrm} scripts
  * Move etc/init.d/live-installer and usr/share/menu/live-installer to debian
    directory as live-installer.init and live-installer.menu respectively.
    There is no way to specify which files installed by dh_installinit and
    dh_installmenu.
  * usr/lib/live-installer/installer.py: init script clean up moved to
    maintainer scripts
  * debian/copyright: update according to latest changes made by me and
    Baurzhan. Also follow DEP5.
  * debian/changelog: fix typos
  * debian/{docs,dirs}: remove it

 -- Timur Birsh <taem@linukz.org>  Sun, 21 Nov 2010 20:27:19 +0600

